<chapter condition="TITLE=Trade Services" id="TS_Main" role="TOPIC">
  <title>Trade Services</title>

  <para role="TEXT">The Trade Services menu on the toolbar, provides
  facilities to manage import and export finances and transactions, through
  the <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>.</para>

  <note>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>The availability of the Trade Services menu and its functions is
        dependent on the permissions assigned to the user. Only those
        functions the user is authorised to use, will be displayed. </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>For the Trade products that are migrated to the Angular
        framework, you need to see
        <emphasis>FCC_modern_trade_client_en.pdf</emphasis>.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </note>

  <para role="TEXT">This menu provides a number of modules, as follows:</para>

