  <para>The Expiry Date validation is not applicable for all status codes of a
  Trade Services transaction. The transactions only with the following status
  codes are validated for correct expiry date:<itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>New</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Amended</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Extended</para>
      </listitem>

